        <div class="row featurette my-4">
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Hey, We provide you the best meal available in your locality. </h2>
            <p class="lead">For the people who live out of their home in another city for their living or students who are studying in another city far from their home, ordering food daily from online services like Zomato/Swiggy or going to eat on any local shop is neither affordable nor feasible. <br>
